respec all

  Run all specs
  
  This is the default command, so running `respec` is the same as `respec all`.

Alias: a

[1mUsage:[0m
  respec [all] [OPTIONS]
  respec all --help | -h

[1mOptions:[0m
  --watch, -w
    Watch for change and rerun
    Conflicts: --repeat

  --repeat, -r
    Wait for a key press after running and repeat
    Conflicts: --watch

  --help, -h
    Show this help
